name: Dandelion Dress
description:
Sweet Summer Dress in a gorgeous Japanese Cotton, in Vintage Posy Print. This Dress features a slim waist tie and ruffle skirt. Available made to order, Please note with production and postage time it may take 2-3 weeks for you to receive your order.

Made In Australia.

POSTAGE AND EXCHANGE 
We use express post (with a tracking number) for our Australian postage, this will be added automatically at the check out, however if you would like to pick up the order just leave a note at the checkout and deduct $8.50 from the total when paying! Overseas postage is $25.00, this will be also be added at the checkout.

We are happy to exchange or give a store credit, within 14 days of purchase, just send an email to thread-designs@bigpond.com.
